name: Whitebubbles
body:
All about Janet 
		
		
	
![](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/13561451/9009165/eca9a6cc-3764-11e5-80c3-1edd3f18578c.png)
              
Hello! My name is Janet Ariana Recendez. I am 17 years old and an incoming senior
at Trinity High School. I love my school because it is an all girls school and no I don't suffer because there are no guys around. I have one younger brother that is 15 that  also goes to a single-gendered school and yes he does suffer     hahaha. I live with my mom,  dad and my cute doggy cookie. I love music and Art as well as running and enjoy
    traveling. Something that is on my bucket list is to travel the world. I love meeting
    new people and learning about different cultures. I think it is exciting to find the 
    similarities and differences we all have. I also started playing around with making 
    websites and I think it is pretty cool too. So I applied to Girls Who Code and now
    I am here learning all about computer science!
